  "title": "Salted vanilla",
  "handle": "salted-vanilla",
  "body_html": "<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The ultimate addictive gourmand—sweet, warm, and instantly recognizable.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s2\">What you’ll smell:</span><span class=\"s1\"><br>It opens with a rich pistachio and almond blend that feels nutty and slightly creamy. Then the salted caramel kicks in—sweet, buttery, and mouthwatering—balanced by a soft floral touch. As it settles, it melts into warm vanilla with a hint of sandalwood, leaving a delicious, beachy-sweet trail.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s2\">Notes:</span></p>\n<ul class=\"ul1\">\n<li class=\"li1\">\n<span class=\"s3\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Top: Pistachio, almond</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li1\">\n<span class=\"s3\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Heart: Heliotrope, jasmine</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li1\">\n<span class=\"s3\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Base: Vanilla, salted caramel, sandalwood</span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s2\">Vibe:</span><span class=\"s1\"><br>Flirty, beachy, and confident. It’s that “hot girl on vacation” energy—fun, glowing, and attention-grabbing.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s2\">When to wear:</span><span class=\"s1\"><br>Perfect for everyday wear, beach days, and summer outings. Works year-round if you love sweet scents, but truly shines in summer when it projects and gets extra creamy on the skin.</span></p>",
